caption: The image is a colorful advertisement for a Japanese food market. The ad features a sushi roll and a fish on top of a rice dish. The text in the image reads "Don't worry eat sushi" and "Fresh, free entry starts at 10:00 am at 123 Any City". The ad is promoting a fresh and free entry event for sushi lovers.
